snippet.title: TurboSquad - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3199540/TurboSquad/

TurboSquad is an action-packed racing game where sabotage takes the wheel! Team up with a quirky AI driver and use traps, wild weapons, and sneaky tactics to outsmart your rivals. Play solo, online, or locally in colorful tracks full of loops, jumps and surprises.
